BEGIN:VEVENT
CATEGORIES:Film / Screening
DESCRIPTION:Triumph of the Heart tells the story of St. Maximilian Kolbe\, 
 a Catholic priest who volunteers to join nine men in a starvation bunker an
 d fights to forge a brotherhood of hope in the darkest place on earth and c
 ulminates in an act of sacrifice that echoes beyond the cell\, illuminating
  hope in one of history’s most horrific chapters.\n\nCo-sponsored with Camp
 us Ministry. For more information and ADA accommodations contact garaventa@
 up.edu and 503-943-7702. Free event.
