BEGIN:VEVENT
CATEGORIES:Academic,Lecture / Presentation / Talk
DESCRIPTION:Join us for this year's Readup author event! University of Port
 land welcomes botanist and professor Robin Wall Kimmerer\, best-selling aut
 hor of Braiding Sweetgrass\, for a lecture and book-signing on March 25. Pa
 rt of the University's Schoenfeldt Distinguished Writers Program\, the even
 t is free and open to the public.
DTEND:20260326T033000Z
DTSTAMP:20260327T022535Z
DTSTART:20260326T023000Z
GEO:45.572074;-122.725955
LOCATION:Buckley Center Auditorium
SEQUENCE:0
